description: The Fountain of Juice is a cold-pressed juice dispensary that hand-crafts pure, raw, organic and medicinal juice potions and nut mylks that are delicious! Our cold pressed juices are made with a rainbow of unadulterated fruits and veggies we get from local farmer’s markets, vegetable stands and cooperatives that source produce from small farms who follow organic growing practices. Our recipes incorporate a nourishing balance of function and flavor, with leafy-green mixes, flu-fighting concoctions and slimming & anti-aging elixirs.
name: The Fountain of Juice
